trans-unit.source: Defines a point, associated with an activity execution status change, to be tracked that is in the potential execution path of a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en plats som är associerad med en aktivitet körning status ändras, spåras som är den potentiella körning sökvägen till en arbetsflödesinstans.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Whenever the execution status of an activity changes, the workflow instance emits an activity status event to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]När körningen status för en aktivitet ändras skickar arbetsflödesinstansen en aktivitets status händelse spårning körningsinfrastrukturen.

trans-unit.source: An ActivityTrackPoint defines a point of interest in the potential execution path of a workflow, qualified by such an activity status event.
trans-unit.target: En ActivityTrackPoint definierar en punkt av intresse för potentiella körning sökvägen till ett arbetsflöde, kvalificerat av sådan aktivitet status händelse.

trans-unit.source: An ActivityTrackPoint contains locations that are included in matching, locations that are excluded from matching, and the data that should be extracted from the workflow instance when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: En ActivityTrackPoint innehåller platser som ingår i matchande och platser som är exkluderade från matchar de data som ska extraheras från arbetsflödesinstansen när punkten spåra matchas.

trans-unit.source: You can add an ActivityTrackPoint to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.ActivityTrackPoints%2A> to instruct the runtime tracking infrastructure to send an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> to the tracking service when the specified set of activity status events occur.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till en ActivityTrackPoint till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.ActivityTrackPoints%2A>instruera spårning körningsinfrastrukturen att skicka en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>till Spårningstjänsten när den angivna uppsättningen aktivitetens statushändelser inträffar.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.ActivityTrackPoints%2A>

trans-unit.source: A single ActivityTrackPoint may be matched at multiple points in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En enda ActivityTrackPoint kan matchas på flera ställen i arbetsflödesinstansen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> contains match conditions for a location or locations in the potential execution path of a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>innehåller matchar villkoren för en plats eller platser i sökvägen för potentiella körningen av en arbetsflödesinstans.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> to define locations that should be included in matching by the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>objekt till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>att definiera platser som ska tas med i matchning av spår.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, you can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> to define locations that should be excluded from matching by the track point.
trans-unit.target: På liknande sätt kan du lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>objekt till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>att definiera platser som ska undantas från matchning av spår.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> to specify data that should be extracted from the workflow instance when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekt och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekt till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>att ange data som ska extraheras från arbetsflödesinstansen när punkten spåra matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: The extracted data will be included in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: Data som extraheras inkluderas i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: You can add to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A> to specify additional information associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>att ange ytterligare information som associeras med TrackPoint.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>

trans-unit.source: These annotations will be included in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> sent when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Dessa anteckningar ska inkluderas i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>skickas när punkten spåra matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes an empty track point.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktorn initierar en tom TrackPoint.

trans-unit.source: No matching locations, excluded locations, data extracts or annotations are specified.
trans-unit.target: Inga matchande platser, exkluderade platser, data extrakt eller anteckningar har angetts.

trans-unit.source: You must configure the track point by adding at least one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du måste konfigurera track-plats genom att lägga till minst en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You may optionally add objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till objekt till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>, och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Annotations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar mängden anteckningar som är associerade med TrackPoint.

trans-unit.source: You can add to Annotations to specify annotations to be returned in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> sent to the tracking service when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till anteckningar för att ange anteckningar som ska returneras i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>skickas till Spårningstjänsten när punkten spåra matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: If Annotations is empty, no annotations are associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Inga kommentarer är associerade med spåra punkten om anteckningar är tom.

trans-unit.source: Annotations are `strings` that you define that contain information associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Anteckningar är `strings` som du definierar som innehåller information som associeras med TrackPoint.

trans-unit.source: For example, an annotation could contain information about the possible execution path the workflow can take from this track point, or it could contain information to be displayed in a user interface.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel en anteckning kan innehålla information om möjliga körning av sökväg som arbetsflödet kan utföra från och med nu spåra eller den kan innehålla information som ska visas i ett användargränssnitt.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of locations that should be excluded from the track point by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar insamling av platser som ska undantas från tidpunkten och spåra genom spårning körningsinfrastrukturen.

trans-unit.source: If any <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> in ExcludedLocations is matched for a particular activity status event, the track point will not be matched and no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> will be sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Eventuella <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>i ExcludedLocations matchas för en viss aktivitet status, spåra punkten inte matchas och inga <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>skickas till Spårningstjänsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: If ExcludedLocations is empty, there are no excluded locations.
trans-unit.target: Om ExcludedLocations är tom, finns det inga uteslutna platser.

trans-unit.source: You can use ExcludedLocations to specifically exclude locations from being tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda ExcludedLocations att uttryckligen exkluderar platser från spåras av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want to track all <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activities except the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activity with an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A> property of "Code1", you can define an <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> that matches all <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activities and add it to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill spåra alla exempelvis <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteter utom de <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktivitet med en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A>egenskapen "Kod1", kan du definiera en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>som matchar alla <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteter och lägga till i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>

trans-unit.source: Then you can define another <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> that matches <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activities with an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A> property set to "Code1" and add it to ExcludedLocations.
trans-unit.target: Kan du ange en annan <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>som matchar <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteter med en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A>egenskapen inställd på "Kod1" och lägga till den ExcludedLocations.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Name%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: The track point will then match all <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity> activities except the "Code1" activity.
trans-unit.target: Spåra punkten kommer sedan att matcha alla <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>aktiviteter utom aktiviteten "Kod1".</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.CodeActivity>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> that specifies locations to be excluded from the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> som anger platser som ska uteslutas från tidpunkten och spåra.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that specifies data to be extracted from the workflow instance and sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar en samling som anger data för att extrahera från arbetsflödesinstansen och skickas till Spårningstjänsten.

trans-unit.source: When a track point is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure can extract data from the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: När en TrackPoint matchas extrahera spårning körningsinfrastrukturen data från arbetsflödesinstansen.

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure encapsulates the extracted data in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> objects that it puts in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A> of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> that it sends to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Spårning körningsinfrastrukturen kapslar in extraherade data i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>objekt som placeras i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A>av den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord>som skickas till Spårningstjänsten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingRecord.Body%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: If Extracts is empty, no data will be extracted.
trans-unit.target: Om extrakt är tomt, extraheras inga data.

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects to Extracts to specify member data that should be extracted from the activity associated with this track point, and you can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects to Extracts to specify member data that should be extracted from the activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekt att analysera att ange medlemsdata som ska extraheras från aktiviteten som är associerad med nu spåra och du kan lägga till <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekt att analysera att ange medlemsdata som ska extraheras från aktiviteten i arbetsflödet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ExtractCollection"></xref> that specifies the data to be extracted and sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ExtractCollection"> </xref> som anger data som ska extraheras och skickas till Spårningstjänsten.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of locations that should be included in matching for the track point by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar insamling av platser som ska tas med i matchande för spåra punkten genom spårning körningsinfrastrukturen.

trans-unit.source: If MatchingLocations is empty, the track point cannot be matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Om MatchingLocations är tom kan inte spåra punkten matchas av körningen spårning infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: You must add at least one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> to MatchingLocations for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> to participate in matching.
trans-unit.target: Du måste lägga till minst en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>till MatchingLocations för den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint>att delta i matchande.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: The track point will be matched if any <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> in MatchingLocations is matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure and no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Spåra punkten matchas eventuella <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>i MatchingLocations matchas av körningsmiljön spårning infrastruktur och ingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>matchas.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> that specifies the locations to be matched for the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> som anger platserna som ska matchas för track-platsen.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är en tom samling.
